name: The Samurai Frog
description:
Heroes of the Far East #1

There is a legend among the adventurers, that deep in the misty mountain there is a village full of amphibian warriors.

A clan of Samurai Frog. Sworn to defend the thousand years old Cherry blossom tree from the outsider. Looking for one of it's sought after branch, that grant eternal life.
